org.jplot2d.element

Interface Colorbar

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, PComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ColorbarEx
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ColorbarImpl

    public interface Colorbar
extends PComponent
    A bar to show a color mapping of image graphs. A colorbar contains 2 axes, innerAxis and outerAxis.

      • getAxisTransform

        @Nonnull
AxisTransform getAxisTransform()
        Return the AxisTransform of this colorbar. The returned AxisTransform is NUMBER-LINEAR, and cannot be changed. The range of returned AxisTransform will be auto-update when the limits of mapping changed.
        Returns:
        the AxisTransform of this colorbar
